-10-04T21:16:48.000Z","msg":"如果去返721前都仲可以諗下....依家不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4840e68e868b11eddee4786eb077c23ee80ed7d0","tid":1623277,"uid":179729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T21:18:42.000Z","msg":"拉"},{"pid":"fd4a8ea833fa429b0ec2b465bd138cc5177beb69","tid":1623277,"uid":326930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T21:22:55.000Z","msg":"回覆＝樓主個名"},{"pid":"f83d6936365a8249f03fa36dd4cca425ac1b675a","tid":1623277,"uid":51171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T21:27:20.000Z","msg":"我覺得可以整個二百萬大遊行扮支持政府，係扮到好認真嗌晒口號咁，等佢放低戒心。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n手足唔好咁on9得唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你估上面咁樣做，政府第二日記招會點講？<br />\n同埋攞到民意授權，佢200%更加瘋狂呀屌你老尾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n長期缺乏認同、支持，一個人先容易崩潰。"},{"pid":"c6160cfb715957eb7cba60f0fcb647db201fec2d","tid":1623277,"uid":155815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T21:31:20.000Z","msg":"你不如話扮放過政府算丫戇鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}